These dataframes are filtered to show the duplications in the raw data from fulcrum or the genotyping sheet. If the dataframe are empty there is no duplication.
Duplication issue 1: 9 collections were two separate isolation records exist for the same c_label.
Solution: Retained the isolation record based on worm presence. Yes > tracks > no.
If both isolation records indicate “tracks only” or “no” then we retain the earliest record.
In no cases did both isolation records indicate worms were present on c_label.
Duplication issue 2: 1 s_label duplicated in the nematode_isolation_s_labeled_plates.csv.
Solution: This duplication is removed in step 5 of process fulcrum script.
